1962;;Phaedra;;American;;Jules Dassin;;Melina Mercouri, Anthony Perkins, Raf Vallone;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phaedra_(film);;Phaedra, second wife of shipping tycoon Thanos (Raf Vallone), falls in love with her husband's son from his first marriage, Alexis (Anthony Perkins). The love is doomed from the very beginning but they are unable to control their feelings.